 recent epoch of tidal interaction between the Magellanic\nClouds. Comparison of the observed properties of RGB stars, in the outer SW\nregion, with N-body simulations shows that the higher RV component in the SW\nregion is at a farther distance than the main body, indicating the presence of\na stellar Counter-Bridge in the SW region of the SMC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Oct 2021 13:40:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
