the one (given\nby Chamseddine [Phys. Rev. D 69 (2004), 024015, hep-th/0309166]) with\nnon-covariant star product.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Oct 2021 13:35:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
